         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility"> ¶ It is my intention, dear friend, to subject the species of the genus  ¶ Erechtites ¶  (as far as it concerns Australia) to a new investigation, ¶  especially since in the last few years much additi...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">76.06.10c</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Johan Lange</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Lange papers, Botanisk Centralbibliotek, Copenhagen.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">Melbourne, 10/6/76</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Es ist meine Absicht, theuerer Freund, die Arten des genus <name key="Erechtites">Erechtites</name> (soweit es Australien angeht) einer neuen Untersuchung zu unterwerfen, zumal da sich in den letzten Jahren viel ergänzendes Material bei mir angehäuft hat, um die Grenzen der Arten besser festzustellen. Würden Sie die Güte haben, mir ein Exemplar Ihrer Schrift zuzusenden, in welcher Sie die mir freundlich zugeignete<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">zugeeignete?</p>
               </note> Art abgebildet haben. Vermuthlich wird sich die Gelegenheit bieten, die mir erwiesene Ehre durch eine Zueignung im selbigen genus zu erwiedern.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Mit Ehrerbietung der Ihre,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Für mehrfache vortreffliche Büchersendungen habe ich Ihnen und Ihren Freunden meinen besten Dank auszusprechen.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">Melbourne, 10/6/76</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It is my intention, dear friend, to subject the species of the genus <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Erechtites">Erechtites</name>
               </seg> (as far as it concerns Australia) to a new investigation,<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">No later treatment of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                        <name key="Erechtites">Erechtites</name>
                     </seg> by M has been found.</p>
               </note> especially since in the last few years much additional material has accumulated at my place, so as to better establish the boundaries of the species. Would you have the goodness to send me a copy of your paper in which you figured the species kindly dedicated to me.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Described as <seg style="font-style: italic; ">E. </seg>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">muelleri</seg>
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>in J. Lange (1861), p. 28, entry number 3; no illustration has been found ( <ref target="http://botanicalillustrations.org/index.php"
                          rend="Internet%20link"
                          style="color: #0563c1; ">
                        <seg rend="Internet%20link" style="color: #0563c1; ">http://botanicalillustrations.org/index.php</seg>
                     </ref>, accessed 7 June 2020).</p>
               </note> Presumably the opportunity will offer itself to reciprocate the honour shown me by a dedication in the same genus.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">With respect your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">I have also to express my best thanks to you and your friends for the repeated excellent sending of books.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Erechtites">Erechtites</name>
            </p>
